Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作點啊,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的情況很危急
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,把眼睛張開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你會回不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟幻人那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是放著不管,梵會…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵會被帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏…應該不是天堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵…回去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作點啊,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了三米特了\N（約地球時間一分半鍾）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少得快幫小瞳急救才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要想辦法,把梵大人給帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有聽到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,拜託您回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是國王,了不起,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多虧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基米爾、達雷特、歇士達、迦迪、比歐雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這種小戰役就送掉性命\N這樣只能被當成是笑話一則嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別扔下我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別扔下我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別扔下我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻弗雷特公國,使我們成功得到能源點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在掛念龍是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍的命運被霧所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模糊不清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我處理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經著手進行下一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把龍給我抓來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我的手握劍會顫抖?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著為他擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但從那之後,他就一直都是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是凡身為劍客,都必須克服的考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾經歷過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自滿與傲慢讓自己陷入恐懼之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近來常找劍客比試的小子,就是你,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒膽跟我打的話,就把錢全都交出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣我就饒你不死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你對自己蠻有信心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報上名來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連·歇薩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一較高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素質不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻僅執著於技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你的劍中看不到光明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必那麼想尋死?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:11:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於沒有家與家人的我,劍就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然輸了我哪還能厚著臉皮繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使劍憊的不是力量也不是技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其真意就在自己本身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好鍛煉你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我與師父巴爾卡斯的相識經過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父他讓當時墮落至極的我,見識了何謂光明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍是用來磨練自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至今我仍無法接近師父的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既了不起又堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人又很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對劍不是很瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想那傢伙一定不會把我的話聽進去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是你說的話,他就一定聽得進去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你人又好又受大家景仰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候你倒挺像惡魔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從幻之月來的小瞳身帶奇妙的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流著龍神人之血的梵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上想要能源點的寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件接著一件發生的奇妙事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏頭一定有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…德萊甸,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝我什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客套話就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟道謝是不用花錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是覺得自己看錯你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才打算來為至今的失禮致歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做事當然都是有目的的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能讓你卸下心防我什麼都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是想要的東西就一定會去奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是以物易物好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是家父留在書房中\N他最後的航海日誌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西對你有用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有用,有用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能就此解開你們身邊的所有謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎團?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是亞特蘭提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:14:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常聽我老爸說你父親一直在找尋亞特蘭提斯的秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我就先借走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還真是有名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連在這種邊境都能讓我顏面無光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和德萊甸代墊的艾斯嘉科尼修理費相比
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來得便宜多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對,確實沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幹嘛那麼多話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直就跟花癡沒兩樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想為我朋友的事問問你的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位朋友有位交往中的男友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個人其實是個花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且竟然還有私生子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差勁透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先聽我說完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻有另一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是個有錢又溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上我那個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那麼明顯了還聽不懂,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我發現對方隱瞞自己\N有孩子的事實跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我就不會再理他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那種男人實在太沒用了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他根本就是來者不拒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…他人很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個不是也很好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表是及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有愛情跟經濟能力對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就決定是他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太算計了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要先腳踏兩條船試試?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不檢點了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要兩邊都放棄算了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲劇女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那…不關我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我那個朋友長久以來的心意怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果問題還是出在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是照自己的心意去做最為自然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來算算看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看哪個人比較適合你那個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面倒是挺準的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你個頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幫人算之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你先搞清楚自己的心意行不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是喜歡梵大人還是亞連啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對梵的感情只是擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心…真的只是那樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就別再接近梵大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不適合亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊,是那個對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在這種地方遇上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就證明了我們有多幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去跟弗肯大人的伴手禮,打聲招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個主意好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果就被我家的婆娘抓包了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫艾斯嘉科尼的人型裝甲就在這裏,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把它交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不照辦的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把你們全宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的…寨巴哈的人型裝甲出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵\N梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去,你還沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵去應戰了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一□氣把它解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部有機可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度竟然解決不了這種貨色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪弗肯大人會對他感到失望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該來做個了結了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢做壞事,你們逃不掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們休想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們休想殺死梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒那個心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,居然目出一隻貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先打到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好您平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人\N梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了,我全都懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不出我所料一切的答案都在幻之谷裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是傳說中龍神人的居住地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歇士達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受引導之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:57.56,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:06.01,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:13.64,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:19.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:22.15,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.39,0:22:27.16,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:31.00,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:34.80,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:38.81,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:42.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:49.78,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:57.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:06.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:13.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:19.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:22.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.39,0:22:27.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:30.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:34.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:38.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:42.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:49.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

